{
  "stem": "1901.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then as soon as we walked through the door-- stop.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "What's your bloody thing doing there?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Yes, we have to bring it in lager because [GERMAN]-- or [? commader, ?] that his name was-- told us that we have to look after it, because it's always damaged every day.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It wasn't true.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And so we walked with that bloody thing for nearly the whole week, up and down and up, and they got used to it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then after, I would say, five or six days, we cleaned the thing out, hosed it out, and we put it full with potatoes and vegetables-- [LAUGHS] mainly potatoes-- and we carried it in camp.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Nobody looked at us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we emptied it in camp, and we had potatoes-- green potatoes and brown potatoes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And we picked them in the-- we had fires, you know-- and we put them in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we divided amongst ourselves.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We were at one barrack, all the Malers in one-- in one.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Block six, I remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we all had to get one, and you one potato, and you one.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And it helps a little bit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "A little bit, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "It was something.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Did they ever find out?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Look, if they find out they kill you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They never found out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we did it for quite awhile.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, a long time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We did it for-- for-- and we went on to-- oh, we worked quite-- I even worked in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, in-- in Birkenau in-- We were very good painters, with a good kommando, and we did quite a few works for the commandant.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Normal, you know, like a house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were in there, and--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You had to be very careful, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Say there was one-- I remember this.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
